234 cocos keeling islands 1 2010 235 christmas island 1 2010 236 bermuda 1 2010 rank code 2054 country comparison :: birth rate this entry gives the average annual number of births during a year per 1,000 persons in the population at midyear also known as crude birth rate <\s>
<s> the birth rate is usually the dominant factor in determining the rate of population growth <\s>
<s> it depends on both the level of fertility and the age structure of the population <\s>
